          <title>A little improvement</title>                                                          <!--[0-1]-->
          <paragraph>Also, Switzerland and Euro Area changed their interest rate in negative for improving economic condition. From the change, Switzerland had a little improvement in import but it has some problems in exports again. Even if BCE needs time to reach a lower unemployment level, the effect of the choice seems positive.</paragraph>                                           <!--[0-N]-->
          <paragraph>In Euro Area the current employment rate is 10.3%, but the forecast is 9.6%</paragraph>                                           <!--[0-N]-->
          <paragraph>In the long term, Switzerland exports previsions will stay at 17043.1 lower than imports.</paragraph>
